Why You're Seeing Repetition
Google News RSS feed is small: ~20-30 results, heavily weighted to top ~5
Articles age out slowly: Takes 1-2 weeks for truly old articles to fall off
No temporal diversity: Your 90-day query returns same top 20, just older
Single keyword: "DJI Dock" is quite specific — broader variants would catch adjacent coverage
No cross-source: Different sources report same events differently
